# libshot

A unified, Wayland/X11-agnostic screen capture library for Linux.

## Installation

```bash
pip install .
```

## Usage

```python
import libshot

# Capture the full screen
image = libshot.capture()

# Capture a specific region
image = libshot.capture(region=(100, 100, 500, 500))

if image:
    image.save("screenshot.png")
```
